# Key role: security_dse_unified_authentication (info only):
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#DCs < 3x nodes use an RF=1
#DCs < 9x nodes use an RF=3
#DCs > 9x nodes use an RF=5
# For the above RF settings see the matching ansible module:
